From the next room, full of the noise of guests, his aunt would plead:

'For goodness' sake, don't lose any of the pieces!' Sometimes his father would come in, look at the puzzle and stretch out a hand tableward, saying: 'Look, this undoubtedly goes in here,' and then Luzhin without looking round would mutter: 'Rubbish, rubbish, don't interfere,' and his father would cautiously apply his lips to 